Using this formula with the given vertices, we have

\begin{align*}
A&=\frac{1}{2}\sqrt{(3-6)^2+(3-5)^2+(1-3)^2}(15-6)\sqrt{(11-5)^2+(9- 3)^2}\\
&=\frac{1}{2}\sqrt{(-3)^2+(-2)^2+(-2)^2}9\sqrt{36+36}\\
